snippet.title: Music for Babies üåô Piano Lullabies üåô Songs of BIrdland & Mozart & Chopin
snippet.description:
Tonight we have wanted to share something very special.

The first three pieces you will hear have been composed and arranged with great love, just like everything we create at Songs of Birdland.

After that, we have let Chopin and Mozart add their timeless touch of magic.

We have made this music to cradle the dreams of little ones, to fill the night with calm and tenderness.

We hope you enjoy it, that it helps babies sleep peacefully, and that it brings everyone a quiet moment of peace.

Thank you for being here and for sharing this little musical corner with us!
